          <para>Show the form to edit the current site by clicking <emphasis role="bold">Site Editor</emphasis> on the administration bar, then
          select <inlinemediaobject>
              <imageobject>
                <imagedata fileref="images/editlayouticon.png" format="PNG"/>
              </imageobject>
            </inlinemediaobject> .</para>
          <mediaobject>
            <imageobject role="html">
              <imagedata width="444" align="center" scale="100" fileref="images/editlayout.png" format="PNG"/>
            </imageobject>
            <imageobject role="fo">
              <imagedata width="444" contentwidth="150mm" align="center" fileref="images/editlayout.png" format="PNG"/>
            </imageobject>
          </mediaobject>
        </step>
        <step>
          <para>The form to edit the current site will appear.</para>
          <mediaobject>
            <imageobject role="html">
              <imagedata width="444" align="center" scale="110" fileref="images/editportalform.png" format="PNG"/>
            </imageobject>
            <imageobject role="fo">
              <imagedata width="444" contentwidth="150mm" align="center" fileref="images/editportalform.png" format="PNG"/>
            </imageobject>
          </mediaobject>
          <para>To edit the configuration and the layout of the current portal, use one of
